I am NOT a racist, nationalist or anything of the kind. I simply made this song because i thought it to be fun and educational to try sampling vocals and put them into a song. For some reason i stumbled over "An Historical Hitler Speach".
Made in Modplug Tracker. 2010 Joel Asplund
(Song disabled by moderation - we don't really need "music" with Hitler speeches or "Sieg Heil" shouts here. Especially not on a server hosted in Germany.)
